text: Chelsea 7750 is a 1913 American silent crime drama movie directed by J. Searle Dawley and is the fourth of the Kate Kirby's Cases detective stories made in 1913. It stars Henry E. Dixey, Laura Sawyer, House Peters, Martin Faust and was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * * Category:1913 movies Category:1910s crime movies Category:1910s drama movies Category:American crime drama movies Category:American silent movies Category:Movies directed by J. Searle Dawley Category:Paramount Pictures movies
